OL,3,CEye tests could be required for older
OL,4,Cdrivers following coroner's report
OL,6,FOlder motorists could be required to
OL,7,Fpass eye tests to keep their driving
OL,8,Flicence, after the government received
OL,9,Fa prevention of future deaths report
OL,10,Ffrom a Lancashire coroner.
OL,12,FEarlier this month Transport Secretary
OL,13,FHeidi Alexander received the report
OL,14,Ffrom HM Senior Coroner for Lancashire
OL,15,FDr James Adeley, which related to the
OL,16,Fdeaths of four people killed by
OL,17,Fdrivers with failing eyesight.
