OL,3,CEye tests could be required for older
OL,4,Cdrivers following coroner's report
OL,6,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander
OL,7,Ftold the Commons Transport Select
OL,8,FCommittee that is something she is
OL,9,F"open to considering" as part of the
OL,10,FGovernment's forthcoming road safety
OL,11,Fstrategy.
OL,13,FAt the inquests in Preston of Marie
OL,14,FCunningham, 79, Grace Foulds, 85,
OL,15,FPeter Westwell, 80, and Anne Ferguson,
OL,16,F75, Dr Adeley described the UK's
OL,17,Flicensing system as "the laxest in
OL,18,FEurope".
