OL,6,FFriends Marie Cunningham and Grace
OL,7,FFoulds were hit by a car while they
OL,8,Fwere out walking together in Birkdale
OL,9,Fon 30 November 2021.
OL,11,FPeter Westwell was hit by 81-year-old
OL,12,Fpensioner Neil Pemberton on 17 March
OL,13,F2022, and had recently stopped driving
OL,14,Fafter his doctor told him to.
OL,16,FAnne Ferguson was struck by a van
OL,17,Fdriven by Vernon Law, 72, in Rochdale,
OL,18,Fon 11 July 2023.
OL,20,FAll four people died as a result of
OL,21,Fthe collisions.
