OL,4,Cdrivers following coroner's report
OL,6,F"Drivers may also admit they drive but
OL,7,Fthen ignore instructions not to drive
OL,8,Fand fail to notify the DVLA."
OL,10,FThe Transport Secretary said: "I know
OL,11,Fthat reading that report will be very
OL,12,Fdistressing for the families of the
OL,13,Fvictims who were killed.
OL,15,F"That, of course, was a situation
OL,16,Fwhere the optician had suggested to
OL,17,F(four) individuals that they needed to
OL,18,Fadvise the authorities that they had a
OL,19,Fmedical condition which affected their
OL,20,Feyesight and where they shouldn't be
OL,21,Fdriving.
