OL,4,Cdrivers following coroner's report
OL,6,F"And of course, that didn't happen. So
OL,7,FI am open to considering the evidence
OL,8,Fon this issue."
OL,10,FAsked when the road safety strategy
OL,11,Fwill be released, Ms Alexander
OL,12,Freplied: "We will be publishing the
OL,13,Ffirst new road safety strategy in 10
OL,14,Fyears, and we hope to publish that
OL,15,Fdocument later this year."
